General.Name: Finders Resources Limited
General.Description: Findi Limited, through its subsidiaries, engages in the development of digital payment systems. The company offers electronic surveillance, managed services space, and end-to-end transaction processing services. It also provides digital banking solutions throught its network of merchants facilitating banking services, utility payments, money transfers, e-commerce, and train and airline tickets payments. The company was formerly known as Vortiv Limited. Findi Limited was incorporated in 1992 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
